  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_3713_14",
    "text": "1．所给关联词将两句话合为句话。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.5409323834520685,
      0.24723115398356557,
      0.7414073240844894,
      0.2686673812075741
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_3713",
    "order": 9
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_3713_15",
    "text": "(1)把杯倒过来。 不会往下流。(即使……也……)",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.5559305086864142,
      0.2765273311897106,
      0.8848893888263967,
      0.3279742765273312
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_3713",
    "order": 10
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_3713_3",
    "text": "面”門国高下國加字的備特德費。【分）",
    "canon_role": "section_header",
    "bbox": [
      0.10048743907011623,
      0.28867452661664883,
      0.3349581302337208,
      0.3101107538406574
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_3713",
    "order": 11
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_3713_4",
    "text": "鸣叫(míng mǐng） 稠密(chóu zhōu） 船舱(cāng chāng） 下垂(chuí cuí) 沟渠(qú  qú ) 宇宙( zòu zhòu )",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.11198600174978128,
      0.31797070382279385,
      0.4729408823897013,
      0.37370489460521616
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_3713",
    "order": 12
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_3713_16",
    "text": "(2)你能认出它。 你不会在夜乱闯。(要是……就……)",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.5559305086864142,
      0.3351196856020007,
      0.901387326584177,
      0.3865666309396213
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_3713",
    "order": 13
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_3713_17",
    "text": "2.根据意思写诗句。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.5399325084364455,
      0.39514112182922473,
      0.6464191976003,
      0.4165773490532333
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_3713",
    "order": 14
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_3713_5",
    "text": "1．在宇宙飞船是shī 重的状态，在yù tǒng 里洗 澡，可不是一件róng yì 的事。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.1124859392575928,
      0.40728831725616294,
      0.477440319960005,
      0.5087531261164702
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_3713",
    "order": 15
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_3713_18",
    "text": "(1)六,西湖的风光景到底和其他时节的不样。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.5564304461942258,
      0.42443729903536975,
      0.9038870141232346,
      0.4751697034655234
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_3713",
    "order": 16
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_3713_19",
    "text": "(2)我坐在窗前,可以望见西岭上堆积着终年不化的积雪,门前停泊 着万外的东吴远来的船只。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.5559305086864142,
      0.48302965344765986,
      0.9043869516310461,
      0.5637727759914255
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_3713",
    "order": 17
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_3713_6",
    "text": "2.在野外，太阳、北极星、jīxuě 都可以当你的xiàng dǎo ,它们都是天然的zhǐnán zhēn ，可以帮 助你辨别向。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.1124859392575928,
      0.5173276170060735,
      0.477440319960005,
      0.6488031439799928
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_3713",
    "order": 18
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_3713_20",
    "text": "1．《晓出净慈寺送林》描写的是秋季早上荷塘的美景。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.539432570928634,
      0.600928903179707,
      0.901387326584177,
      0.6230796713111826
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_3713",
    "order": 19
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_3713_21",
    "text": "2．《雷》是按照雷前、雷中、雷后的顺序写的。 (",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.539432570928634,
      0.6302250803858521,
      0.9008873890763655,
      0.6516613076098606
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_3713",
    "order": 20
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_3713_22",
    "text": "3.为了便航天员在舱体中活动,宇宙飞船的舱壁上安装了许多特制 扶或设施，让他们稳定体。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.5389326334208224,
      0.6602357984994641,
      0.9038870141232346,
      0.7116827438370846
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_3713",
    "order": 21
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_3713_7",
    "text": "(竟竞) (绝决) (永泳) (提题) (密宝) (辨辩)边 指点 窗户 忠实的 事情 解决 吸管 清新的 向导 安装 方向 有趣的 杯子 打开 难题 普通的 空气",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.1124859392575928,
      0.6852447302608075,
      0.4584426946631671,
      0.7717041800643086
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_3713",
    "order": 22
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_3713_23",
    "text": "4.《悯农》(其）诗中“四海闲,农夫犹饿死”反映出当时残酷的 现实：农民苦劳作，成果却被他抢去了。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.5389326334208224,
      0.7195426938192212,
      0.9033870766154231,
      0.7702750982493748
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_3713",
    "order": 23
  },
  {
