  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_3713_24",
    "text": "看天预报，回答下列问题。（填序号)",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.5409323834520685,
      0.8074312254376563,
      0.7394075740532433,
      0.8288674526616648
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_3713",
    "order": 25
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_3713_25",
    "text": "1.班计划星期六去春游，师说如果下就不去了。明明回家赶快看天 预报,他们能去春游吗? （)(2分）",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.5389326334208224,
      0.8367274026438014,
      0.9043869516310461,
      0.8881743479814219
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_3713",
    "order": 26
  },
  {
